Uhura，我很抱歉
Uhura, I'm sorry.

47
00:04:14,337 --> 00:04:15,755
Spock，我们要回到企业号上
Spock, we're going back to the <i>Enterprise.</i>

48
00:04:15,797 --> 00:04:16,798
我们会把你弄出来的
<i>We'll get you out of there.</i>

49
