- Hold on, wee man!

79
00:06:43,069 --> 00:06:44,571
你说的可是那座活火山
You're talking about an active volcano!

80
00:06:44,654 --> 00:06:46,239
长官，如果那个东西爆发了
Sir, if that thing erupts,

81
