<i>has successfully detonated.</i>

108
00:09:26,566 --> 00:09:28,651
你听到没有，祝贺你Spock
<i>You hear that? Congratulations, Spock.</i>

109
00:09:29,736 --> 00:09:31,071
你刚刚拯救了他们的世界
You just saved the world.

110
00:09:31,321 --> 00:09:33,073
你违反了原则
You violated the Prime Directive.

111
00:09:33,281 --> 00:09:35,742
哦，拜托，Spock。他们看见我们了，多大个事儿啊
Oh, come on, Spock. They saw us. Big deal.

